{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC04_JUR_090.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x28,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Well, to celebrate exterminating the wolf, this is on me today. Eat and drink all you want!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x182,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, hunting that big thing down is quite an accomplishment."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I did have Ayesha's help.<CR>It was a tough opponent."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Mmhm. When I saw him in the plaza,<CR>I honestly got the chills."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I thought, \"Ahh, thank goodness I'm not a huntsman. I'm really glad I'm the owner of a tavern.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "M-Me, too. I'm glad I'm an apothecary..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "A-Although, I did end up helping out, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "So Juris, are you always fighting strong enemies like him?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "No, it's not too often that I go up against tough ones like him."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "It's been a while since I felt the tension of hunt or be hunted like that. "
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "That wolf is totally the talk of the town."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x182,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Especially since this time, the town felt some damage. So Juris, you're a rather famous hero now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Stop that, I'm just a huntsman.<CR>I'm not that kind of a person."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "However, you failed at the very end. I mean, you didn't bring back any proof that you exterminated it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "It was a whopper. You should've at least brought back its fur."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Did you sympathize with your prey? That's not like you, Juris..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that's, umm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "He was a hunter. I wanted to at least protect his dignity."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "That's right. It didn't feel right to bring his fur back as a war trophy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "So we buried him in a grave."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x141,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Seriously!? What a waste..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x143,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "With fur like that, it would've gone for a high value. That's not like you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "About that... How can I say it?<CR>It's not Juris's fault..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I thought...that maybe...it would be better to do it like that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, that was your suggestion!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Umm...yes. Did I do something wrong...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Nooo, absolutely not! Yup, I think that was an excellent idea."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Even if your opponent was a beast,<CR>its dignity should be protected!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Kyle, it seems like you're saying something completely different than before..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "No, well, thinking deeper about it, it seems like it's a praiseworthy act."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "But maybe I was a bit presumptuous..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Don't worry! You're completely fine! What you did was glorious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Goodness, Kyle..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, Ayesha, I think that what you're saying may be right..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "I think it was appropriate to protect his dignity."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Especially since his dignity was trampled on when we made a spectacle of him in the plaza."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "It was the best way to make an apology."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "Well, for the time being, let's have a drink to celebrate the extermination of the wolf!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x182,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "No more gloomy stuff like this,<CR>cuz that would be a waste!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "...You're right. Well, back to the celebration...cheers!"
        }
    ]
}